s=\"gi-breadcrumb__link\" data-template=\"home\" href=\"https://www.southhams.gov.uk/\">Home</a>\t\t\t\t\t\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"gi-breadcrumb__item\">\n                <a class=\"gi-breadcrumb__link\" data-template=\"list\" href=\"https://www.southhams.gov.uk/OurServices\">Our Services</a>\t\t\t\t\t\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"gi-breadcrumb__item\">\n                <a class=\"gi-breadcrumb__link\" data-template=\"list\" href=\"https://www.southhams.gov.uk/recyclingwaste\">Waste and Recycling Service</a>\t\t\t\t\t\n        </li>\n</ol>\n</nav>\n\n</div>\n</div> -->\n\n\n<div class=\"lgd-region lgd-region--breadcrumb region region-breadcrumb\" style=\"margin-bottom:0px;\">\n        <div class=\"lgd-container padding-horizontal\">\n                <div class=\"lgd-region__inner lgd-region__inner--breadcrumb\">\n                        <div id=\"block-localgov-southhams-localgov-breadcrumbs-base\" class=\"block block-system block-system-breadcrumb-block\">\n                                <nav class=\"breadcrumbs\" aria-labelledby=\"system-breadcrumbs\">\n                                        <ol class=\"breadcrumbs__list\">\n                                                <li class=\"breadcrumbs__item\">\n                                                        <a class=\"breadcrumbs__link\" href=\"https://www.southhams.gov.uk/\">Home</a>\n                                                </li>\n                                                <li class=\"breadcrumbs__item\">\n                                                        <a class=\"breadcrumbs__link\" href=\"https://www.southhams.gov.uk/OurServices\">Our Services</a>\n                                                </li>\n                                                <li class=\"breadcrumbs__item\">\n                                                        <a class=\"breadcrumbs__link\" href=\"https://www.southhams.gov.uk/recyclingwaste\">Waste and Recycling Service</a>\n                                                </li>\n                                        </ol>\n                                </nav>\n                        </div>\n                </div>\n        </div> \n</div>\n\n<!-- <div class=\"lgd-region lgd-region--breadcrumb region region-breadcrumb\" style=\"background-color:#f92b2b;padding:30px 10px;color: white;font-weight: 600;\">\n        <div class=\"lgd-container padding-horizontal\">\n                <div class=\"lgd-region__inner lgd-region__inner--breadcrumb\">\n                        <div id=\"block-localgov-southhams-localgov-breadcrumbs-base\" class=\"block block-system block-system-breadcrumb-block\">\n                        <p>We are making changes to our web pages on Friday 17th November in preparation for the roll out of our new refuse and recycling rounds. Our online services will be unavailable until Saturday 18th November.</p>\n                        <p>Please visit our <a href=\"https://www.southhams.gov.uk/waste-and-recycling\" style=\"color: white;\">Waste & Recycling Page</a> for further information.</p>\n                        <p>We thank you for your patience.</p>\n\n\n                        </div>\n                </div>\n        </div> \n</div> -->\n<div class=\"pagetitle\">\n    <div class=\"lgd-container\">\n        <h1 class=\"pagetitle__heading\">\n            <span>Find your Recycling and Waste collection day</span>\n        </h1>\n    </div>\n</div> <div class=\"maincontent\" role=\"main\" id=\"maincontent\">\n    <div class=\"lgd-container content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"lgd-row\">\n            <div class=\"lgd-row__two-thirds\">\n\n                \n                <h2>If you are unsure when your next collection day is then you can find it here.</h2>\n\n                <!-- <div class=\"collectionDiv\">\n                    <h3>Notice:</h3>\n                    <p>\n                        Please be aware that our planned suspension of garden waste runs from Monday the 18th December and begins again on Monday 15th January.\n                    </p>\n                </div> -->\n\n                <p>Please use the information detailed below to see what collections are available at your property, and the day we will be collecting. All properties are now able to have recycling boxes, reusable white sack for plastics and a food caddy.</p>\n                <p>If you have subscribed to the garden waste service, please be aware this collection may be on a different day to your refuse and recycling service. Our garden collections are suspended for 4 weeks over the festive period.</p>\n                <p>If you require further information about any of our services, please visit our Waste and Recycling page.</p>\n                <p>During peak season periods, collections may occur before 7am.</p>\n                <p>Enter your postcode in the 'Postcode' box, click the 'Find Address' button and select your address from the 'Address' drop down list.</p>\n\n                <form action=\"https://waste.southhams.gov.uk/mycollections\" id=\"wdshInit\" method=\"post\" accept-charset=\"utf-8\">\n                                                <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"fcc_session_token\" value=\"0b74bd7f9844e1c52e14bd70950c6fa7\" />\n                    <div class=\"icmform icmformleft\">\n                        <ol>\n                            <li>\n                                <fieldset class=\"icmvertical icmhideborder\">\n                                    <legend><span>Search For Your Address</span></legend>\n                                    <ol>\n                                        <li>\n                                            <fieldset class=\"icmvertical addresslookup icmhide\">\n                                                <ol>\n                                                    <li>\n                                                        <div class='field_addresslookup fielddiv_icmstext clear'> \n                             